name: Comwin Hong Kong Ltd.
tag_list: usb-flash-drive, power-bank, external-hard-disk, memory-cards, usb-hub, ipad-accessories, iphone-accessoires, speakers
overview:
Comwin Hong Kong Ltd. specialised in producing and exporting computer, mobile phone related products and electronic gifts such as USB flash drive, memory cards, external hard disk, LED lamp, and power bank, etc.

Comwin Hong Kong can offer much more products (you can see more proucts from their website: www.comwin-online.com) with Chinese factory price. They offer much better price if you send inquiries to their email box sales@comwin-hk.com.

Benefit from their forwarder which is one of biggest agent of DHL, UPS, TNT, FedEx in Shenzhen, we saved a lot freight cost.

It’s cool to purchase some electronic products such as USB flash drive, LED light, USB hub, computer mouse as promotional gifts from Comwin Hong Kong Ltd directly. It do save cost.
